Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:04.23,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Encounters are mysterious!\NBut the world is even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:10.13,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's an author mystery!\NSome mysteries exist outside of writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:13.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:02:01.57,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I, Samonji Matsuda, have solved tonight's bloody string of murders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:07.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That person is undoubtedly the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:07.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}"Detective Samonji"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The son! The son! The son did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's dumb! The son is a fake! It's the wife of the murdered man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you think did it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say the same person as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See! Even he thinks so!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would he know? Kids don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:40.58,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:45.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...is you, his son!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- I knew it!\N- That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was different the last time I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Samonji series is always being remade,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the killer changes each time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why it's always so interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was that for?! Don't make me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.58,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quick-draw detective, my butt! How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turn it back! Samonji's about to pull out his sword and say a haiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Turn it back! It's going to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:35.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Things sure are peaceful for father and daughter to argue over this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:41.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So many people have fallen victim to their organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:45.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But nobody realizes it's the organization's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:48.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I want to be normal again,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:53.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have to turn this bumbling detective into a real master detective
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:59.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and obtain information on the men in black's organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:05.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he gets more work, I'll eventually run into a case involving them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:12.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I continue to seek the truth, I know I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so good about it anyway? He's just a third-rate detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:26.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So says the dimwitted detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, the original series ended long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's annoying that they keep putting it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, they started the serials again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see. I'm sure it's around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Literature Era started it two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Nintaro Shinmei's highly anticipated 'Detective Samonji' returns!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He and a killer disappeared into a fire 10 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I guess he survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It takes you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r} said on the phone the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That mystery nerd, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? I think someone's at your office downstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, tell them it's late and to come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! The office is closed for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I really do need to talk to Detective Mouri about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he at least hear what I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hottie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rather late, so could you come back tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying to our guest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting! I am Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for my rude daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please! Come right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.\N- Right this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude? You told me to turn her away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies! Go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- It's nothing special, but...\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, then. May I ask what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. My name is Kaori Shinmei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Kaori Shinmei"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Shinmei? You don't mean...?!\N- The mystery writer's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:03.04,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaori Shinmei (22)\NOffice worker
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Nintaro Shinmei is my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the daughter of that great master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can never get enough of Samonji's haikus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how can I help you? Does he want to use me in a novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, actually... My father has been missing for two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- He's...\N- ...missing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}is{\i0} quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been writing serials for Literature Era for the past two months!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's the truth! He and my mother disappeared from their home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Your mother, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They both vanished about one week before this serialization began.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked with all our relatives and acquaintances of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but no one knew anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, don't his serials mean that he {\i1}is{\i0} writing manuscripts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oddly enough, the manuscripts are faxed to the editing department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every Saturday, at exactly midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't the faxes have the sender's phone number or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the sender has it configured not to display those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably because he and his wife are on vacation somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he sends the faxes from the hotel they're staying at!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought so too at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they've never been quiet for two months like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only think that something happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you contact the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked them to investigate, but there had been no ransom calls
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the manuscripts were being sent, so they said not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried the other detective agencies, but they all said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're my last hope, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're only wasting time by sitting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's check the editing department where his manuscripts get sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can save your troubles for after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Shinmei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s manuscripts get sent here every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:11.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Daigakukan"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More should be sent today, at any time now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are these manuscripts really written by him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Although they're typed out, the words are most definitely his!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He signs his name next to the title each time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can show you the faxed manuscripts, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Halves at the Top"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The title is "Halves at the Top"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he's signed them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you certain this is his signature?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. We confirmed it when I came here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about, Kaori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's just so focused on writing that he forgot to contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same thing happens to lots of other writers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But are you sure he forgot? His wife's with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he seem different in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Different?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, like during a meeting or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we had a simple meeting before we started the serials,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he didn't seem any different...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything at all? Even the tiniest thing might help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose there is the fact he restarted his Detective Samonji series.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, I asked him to restart this series for the past four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he always answered by saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:06.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Samonji is dead. There's no bringing him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I had half given up when he suddenly called two months ago
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to ask if we could make room for his new Samonji series.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were more than happy to oblige, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we hurriedly canceled the new series we were running
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and replaced it with Samonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come to think of it, this doesn't pertain to him exactly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but for the dedication, he wrote this:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Attention, all master detectives throughout Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you wish to surpass my intellect, solve this case's {\i1}true{\i0} mystery."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's quite a provocative dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. And ever since the first chapter, we've received
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,tons of calls and fan letters saying, "This is how it was done!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As an editor, it makes me happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it seemed like a rare move for such a mild-mannered writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though, fans {\i1}have{\i0} been waiting like crazy for over 10 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so it's only natural he's getting such a big reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Like crazy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, there was even a scary call last year from a crazed fan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who threatened to set this place on fire if he didn't restart the series!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about extreme...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! There's one other thing that seemed strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He appears in his own novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinmei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} appears in the story, as an old friend of Samonji's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a struggling writer who resides in France.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are about 40 stories in the series, but this is a first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's going to end with all the previous cases
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,being things Samonji told him about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kind of like how Watson is to Sherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say! Could you show me that scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But can you read kanji, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right! Here he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinmei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} makes his first appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when Samonji calls a friend living in France for advice on a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His character is absentminded and funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10:00 is written in kanji here, but 1:00 is written with a number!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy must've been pretty tired, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}is{\i0} strange. Could this actually be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...a misprint on your part?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wanted to fix it to make it easier to read, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he said, "The lay of the letters is a novel's life! Don't change it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it many times before the serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also said he'd cancel the series immediately if we defied his wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then that makes it all the odder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:44.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's almost as if something is being hidden in the writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:49.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then there are Shinmei{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sensei{\r\be10}'s signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:54.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If my theory is correct, it's possible that he's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:16:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Here's his latest fax!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't look yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a mystery story! Wait until it's in book form to read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his signature is weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chapters 6 through 8 match perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.61,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Nintaro"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-They do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chapters 1 through 6 are all slightly different, though. I wonder why!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He obviously just copied an earlier signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he didn't want to write it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...or he couldn't anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he can't write anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that means Shinmei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} might already be dead, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad! This requires immediate action!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You! The police! Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:21.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's not 100% yet! There's a chance he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:28.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The key to saving his life is probably hidden inside this novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:32.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As a message he's left for us detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Daigakukan"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't open an investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we still can't. Not at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nintaro Shinmei, her father and a mystery writer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,has been missing for two months now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, his wife is also gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only think they got caught up in some sort of incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, his manuscripts {\i1}are{\i0} being faxed here every single week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though they're faxes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his daughter and the editors all agree it's his writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And like I said, those faxes are the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't those signatures seem strange to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Signatures? But they were already confirmed to be his.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between Chapter 1 and 6, his signatures are all slightly different,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but between Chapter 6 and 8, they're all exactly the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're obviously copies of a previous signature
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and evidence that he's now in a condition in which he can't write!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:19:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, something has happened to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then tell me... Who did what to Mr. Shinmei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd believe you more if there was a threatening phone call,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there's been nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, maybe he got sick of signing them and used copies instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:25.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}True. Given the circumstances, Inspector Megure is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:29.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It wouldn't be surprising for an eccentric writer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:35.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to take his wife and hole up somewhere to focus on his writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:41.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But something bugs me! It wasn't like him to write that dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:46.64,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Attention, all master detectives throughout Japan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:46.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It was very extreme and provocative for someone so mild-mannered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:51.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then, there's the fact the writer suddenly appears in the series.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:56.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then there's his odd dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:03.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}that mixes numbers, kanji numbers, and English letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If my theory is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:10.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}there must be a message from Shinmei{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sensei{\r\be10} in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! I made copies of all the lines Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was curious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shinmei makes four appearances so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have a copy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop that! Don't get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay! There are extras!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Here you go!\N- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, his first appearance is when the main detective character
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,calls Mr. Shinmei, who is residing in France.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's also in France the second time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's in France the third time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the fourth time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does Mr. Shinmei like France?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. He and my mother often traveled there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:08.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn! Reading them backwards or rearranging them doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:11.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If only I had a point to start from!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, do you mind if we use Chapter 8 of "Halves at the Top,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the manuscript he just faxed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Halves at the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the title of the work you're reading right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:28.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Halves at the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:33.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Halves at the top?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:38.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on, now! Could this actually be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:46.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:52.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's a message from Shinmei{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sensei{\r\be10} hidden in these lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:57.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which makes it all fit: that provocative dedication,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:02.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the author's appearance in the story, and the odd lines of dialogue!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:09.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what is the goal of the person holding him and his wife captive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this manuscript! There's more dialogue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is the eighth chapter that was just faxed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:58.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Hurry..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.53,0:24:00.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"There's..."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.09,0:24:01.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"...no time..."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Hurry, there's no time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:14.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.08,0:24:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: French
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:21.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A message from the creator, Aoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.83,0:24:23.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What, did he say this corner's popular?
